{"tid":1994021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"新加坡首季失業率升至金融海嘯後最高","createTime":"2020-04-29T07:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T11:11:14.000Z","uid":166360,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"7e0884d99cf11aaa229b7ce00c8721a3e0fc130b","tid":1994021,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:38:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">新加坡人力部公布，首季失業率升至2.4%</span>，按季上升0.1個百分點，創09年金融海嘯後最高；剔除外籍家庭傭工後總就業人數減少近2萬人，是03年非典疫情後最大季度跌幅，因為製造業、服務業及建築業等行業聘請外勞人數大幅減少。<br />\n<br />\n數字又顯示，首季裁員人數升至3千人。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡政府警告，受新型肺炎疫情打擊，就業市場情況可能進一步惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523411-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523411-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=79c24feb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523411-20200429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b4d3c9b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523411-20200429.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">同期香港失業率為4.2%</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521642-20200420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521642-20200420.htm&d=JNpWH9nW0yy7OMfwbmfjw7HKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=cbafdfb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521642-20200420.htm&h=f83b58a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521642-20200420.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e7a747964d97120f33da52ab87e006b54c64732f","tid":1994021,"uid":504,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7